\[
\E_{y\in B_{\infty}(x,r_{1})}\E_{z\in B_{\infty}(y,r_{2})}\norm{\nabla f(z)-g(y)}_{1}\leq n^{3/2}\frac{r_{2}}{r_{1}}L
